import React from 'react'
import AnimePanel from '../AnimePanel'
import Header from '../Header'
import Popular from '../Popular'
import Trending from '../Trending'

export default function Home() {
  return (
    <React.Fragment>
      <Header></Header>
      <Trending></Trending>
      <Popular></Popular>
      <AnimePanel></AnimePanel>
    </React.Fragment>
  )
}
